quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  7,59,"Indeed, We sent Noah to his people. He said, “O my people, worship Allah; you have no god other than Him. I fear for you the punishment of a momentous Day.”"
  7,60,"The chiefs of his people said, “We certainly see that you are clearly misguided.”"
  7,61,"He said, “O my people, I am not misguided, but I am a messenger from the Lord of the worlds"
  7,62,"I convey to you the messages of my Lord and give you sincere advice, and I know from Allah what you do not know"
  7,63,"Are you surprised that a reminder should come to you from your Lord through a man from among yourselves, so that he may warn you and you may fear Allah, and so that you may be shown mercy?”"
  7,64,"But they rejected him, so We delivered him and those who were with him in the Ark, and We drowned those who rejected Our signs. They were indeed people who were blind [to the truth]"